### GET request to load all steam app ids
GET https://api.steampowered.com/ISteamApps/GetAppList/v0002/?key=STEAMKEY&format=json

### GET request to load single steam app
GET https://store.steampowered.com/api/appdetails?appids={{appId}}&key={{apikey}}

### GET game list
GET https://api.steampowered.com/IStoreService/GetAppList/v1/?include_games=true&key={{apikey}}&max_results=50000

### GET game list paging, if "have_more_results === true"
GET https://api.steampowered.com/IStoreService/GetAppList/v1/?include_games=true&key={{apikey}}&max_results=50000&
    last_appid=1533580

### GET game reviews, skip details
GET https://store.steampowered.com/appreviews/{{appId}}?json=1&num_per_page=0&language=all&purchase_type=all&
    key={{apikey}}

### Get player summaries
GET https://api.steampowered.com/ISteamUser/GetPlayerSummaries/v0002/?key={{appId}}&steamids={{steamId}}
